    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ApplicationCreateRequest
    This class represents the request body for creating an application in the Green Global Initiative API.
    ApplicationDetails
    This class represents the entity for the application details in the Green Global Initiative API.
    ApplicationDetailsDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the details of a grant application.
    ApplicationDetailsRepo
    Repository interface for performing CRUD operations on ApplicationDetails.
    ApplicationUpdateRequest
    This class represents the request body for updating an application in the Green Global Initiative API.
    ContactUs
    This class represents the entity for the "contact_us" table in the Green Global Initiative API database.
    ContactUsRepo
    Repository interface for handling CRUD operations related to the ContactUs entity.
    DevCorsConfig
    Development-specific CORS configuration class.
    GlobalExceptionController
    A global exception handler for the application.
    Grants
    Represents a grant available under the Green Global Initiative.
    GrantsApplicationController
    REST controller for managing grants applications.
    GrantsApplicationService
    Service interface for handling grants application details.
    GrantsApplicationServiceImpl
    Service implementation for handling operations related to grant applications.
    GrantsController
    REST controller for managing grants in the Nausicaä Global Green Initiative API.
    GrantsDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for Grants.
    GrantsRepo
    Repository interface for interacting with the 'Grants' entity in the database.
    GrantsService
    Service interface for managing grants-related operations.
    GrantsServiceImpl
    Service implementation for handling operations related to grants.
    JwtFilter
    JwtFilter is a custom filter used to authenticate JWT tokens in HTTP requests.
    JwtUtil
    JwtUtil is a utility class for handling JWT operations such as token generation, token validation, and extraction of user information from the token.
    LoginRequest
    This class represents the request body for a login request in the Green Global Initiative API.
    NausicaaGreenInitiativeApplication
    Main entry point for the Nausicaa Green Initiative Application.
    QueryController
    REST controller for handling "Contact Us" queries in the Nausicaä Global Green Initiative API.
    QueryCreateRequest
    This class represents the request body for creating a query in the Green Global Initiative API.
    QueryService
    Service interface for handling operations related to user queries.
    QueryServiceImpl
    Service implementation for handling operations related to user queries.
    ResourceNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when a requested resource is not found.
    SecurityConfig
    Security configuration class for the application.
    UserController
    REST controller for managing users in the Nausicaä Global Green Initiative API.
    UserDetails
    Represents the user details in the Green Global Initiative application system.
    UserDetailsDto
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) for User Details.
    UserDetailsRepo
    Repository interface for interacting with the UserDetails entity in the database.
    UserService
    Service interface for managing user-related operations.
    UserServiceImpl
    Implementation of the UserService interface for managing user-related operations.
